·盖拉（Sarah Michelle Gellar）曾请假去看泰勒·斯威夫特（Taylor Swift）的“Eras”巡演的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Sarah-Michelle-Gellar-and-Taylor-Swift.-CREDIT_-Kristina-Bumphrey_Variety-via-Getty-Images-and-Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Sarah-Michelle-Gellar-and-Taylor-Swift.-CREDIT_-Kristina-Bumphrey_Variety-via-Getty-Images-and-Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Sarah-Michelle-Gellar-and-Taylor-Swift.-CREDIT_-Kristina-Bumphrey_Variety-via-Getty-Images-and-Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Sarah-Michelle-Gellar-and-Taylor-Swift.-CREDIT_-Kristina-Bumphrey_Variety-via-Getty-Images-and-Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Sarah-Michelle-Gellar-and-Taylor-Swift.-CREDIT_-Kristina-Bumphrey_Variety-via-Getty-Images-and-Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Sarah-Michelle-Gellar-and-Taylor-Swift.-CREDIT_-Kristina-Bumphrey_Variety-via-Getty-Images-and-Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Sarah-Michelle-Gellar-and-Taylor-Swift.-CREDIT_-Kristina-Bumphrey_Variety-via-Getty-Images-and-Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sarah-michelle-gellar">莎拉·米歇尔·盖拉</a>透露，她曾请一天假，以便参加<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>的“Eras”巡演。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/taylor-swift-eras-tour-end-impact-3820896">泰勒·斯威夫特的 Eras 巡演结束：看看其巨大的全球影响力</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位女演员目前正在与她的搭档<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/christian-slater">克里斯蒂安·史莱特</a>一起宣传《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/watch-the-first-trailer-for-dexter-original-sin-prequel-series-3793241"><em>嗜血法医</em>》前传系列剧<em>《嗜血法医：原罪》</em></a> 。</p><p>在接受<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=or4yp7D_bdM" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《德鲁·巴里摩尔秀》</em></a>采访时，她透露自己十月份曾前往迈阿密观看斯威夫特最后一场“Eras”演出，并称这场表演“令人难以置信”。</p><p>她又补充说，为了能有机会去拍戏，她不断地请假。 “他知道这是我在工作中唯一关心的事情，”她说，指的是斯莱特。 “我想，我只需要周五休息。”她告诉巴里摩尔，节目组想知道她是否需要休息一天来照顾孩子。</p><p> “嗯，我要去迈阿密观看 Eras 巡演，”她回忆道。 “我在洛杉矶看过，但她没有拍《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-the-tortured-poets-department-lyrics-tracklist-3619454">折磨诗人部</a>》。所以，我想去看看《受折磨的诗人》，然后我就去见了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/florence-welch">弗洛伦斯·韦尔奇</a>。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-florence-welch-join-taylor-swift-for-the-second-time-on-the-eras-tour-3804279">韦尔奇与斯威夫特一起在舞台上合唱了他们合作的曲目“Florida！！！”</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/florence-and-the-machine">Florence + The Machine</a>音乐家在“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-the-tortured-poets-department-lyrics-tracklist-3619454">The Tortured Poets Department</a> ”曲目的第二节中加入了她。</p><p>在此之前，盖拉曾于 2023 年 8 月《折磨的诗人部门》上映之前去见过斯威夫特。当时，她在 Instagram 上分享了一篇帖子，写道：“正式进入我的时代”，并展示了她在巡演中佩戴的友谊手镯。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CvnDgZAx3GS/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: 